 Britford, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 100."},"et":{"1190–1290":"1190–1290","1250–Male":"1250–Surnud","1165–Male":"1165–Surnud","1170–Female":"1170–Surnud","1190":"1190","1165":"1165","1250":"1250","1170":"1170","1290":"1290","Britford, Wiltshire, England":"Britford, Wiltshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Hampshire, England":"Hampshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1190–1290":"1190–1290","1250–Male":"1250–Kuollut","1165–Male":"1165–Kuollut","1170–Female":"1170–Kuollut","1190":"1190","1165":"1165","1250":"1250","1170":"1170","1290":"1290","Britford, Wiltshire, England":"Britford, Wiltshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Hampshire, England":"Hampshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1190–1290":"1190–1290","1250–Male":"1250–Décédé","1165–Male":"1165–Décédé","1170–Female":"1170–Décédée","1190":"1190","1165":"1165","1250":"1250","1170":"1170","1290":"1290","Britford, Wiltshire, England":"Britford, Wiltshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Hampshire, England":"Hampshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Peter Kingsmill est né en 1190, à Hampshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, son père, Hue de Kingsmill, avait 25 ans et sa mère, Margaret de Beaumont, avait 21 ans. Il a eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé en 1290, à Britford, Wiltshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, à l’âge de 100 ans."},"de":{"1190–1290":"1190–1290","1250–Male":"1250–Verstorben","1165–Male":"1165–Verstorben","1170–Female":"1170–Verstorben","1190":"1190","1165":"1165","1250":"1250","1170":"1170","1290":"1290","Britford, Wiltshire, England":"Britford, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom","Hampshire, England":"Hampshire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Als Peter Kingsmill 1190 in Hampshire, England, United Kingdom geboren wurde, war sein Vater Hue de Kingsmill 25 und seine Mutter Margaret de Beaumont 21. Er hatte mindestens 1 Sohn. Er starb 1290 im Alter von 100 Jahren in Britford, Wiltshire, England, United Kingdom."},"ht":{"1190–1290":"1190–1290","1250–M